果。",{"url":51,"title":52,"date":53,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":54,"description":55,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200721\u002F1935618580\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (24) - AnimatedSprite","2020-07-21 20:49:21",[13,14,11,15,5],"Pixi 是一套很適合製作 2D 動畫的一個框架，那麼又該如何在 Pixi 撰寫動畫呢?",{"url":57,"title":58,"date":59,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":60,"description":61,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200715\u002F1008641235\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (23) - dat.GUI","2020-07-15 12:55:28",[13,14,11,15,5],"接下來這一篇就要來實際加入 dat.GUI。",{"url":63,"title":64,"date":65,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":66,"description":67,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200707\u002F621122962\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (22) - debug","2020-07-07 13:29:11",[13,14,11,15,5],"接下來我們來認識一下該如何在 Pixi 上 debug。",{"url":69,"title":70,"date":71,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":72,"description":73,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200701\u002F237553233\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (21) - 碰撞邊界(3)","2020-07-01 15:30:15",[13,14,11,15,5],"這一篇會稍微接續上一篇的部分小地方來做修正與說明，所以大多程式碼會以上一篇為主，所以這一篇會稍微短一點。",41,5,{"postCount":77,"tagCount":78},1035,1009,1784010313555]